data.description: Location, location, location! Just 25 minutes from Tesla's Austin Gigafactory and 30 minutes from Austin Airport. Conveniently positioned minutes from shopping, restaurants, grocery, parks and essentials near Hwy 71. Travel anywhere with ease while being tucked away from the hustle and bustle. Charming, very well maintained 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom, single-story home featuring a 2-car attached garage! Large living room with fireplace adjoining the kitchen is perfect for entertaining with access to the backyard and patio for an additional gathering area. Master bedroom with vaulted ceiling and large walk-in closet. Master bathroom has 2 sinks, separate tub and shower. Fully fenced backyard. Stainless steel appliances, refrigerator stays. This beautiful one story home with 4 bedrooms will not last, come check it out!
